    "lines": [
      "# Spaced Retrieval Practice",
      "",
      "Spaced repetition, 中文间隔复习, schedules recall near the predicted forgetting point.",
      "",
      "## Evidence",
      "",
      "检索练习效应表明主动回忆比重复阅读更能巩固长期记忆。",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "Distributed practice, spaced practice, and 分散复习 are related terms with different emphasis.",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "A scheduling model must separate retrieval success from mere card exposure."
    ],
